             [38;5;229mAutomated Firewall Policy Validator[0m

[38;5;39m──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[0m

This is an open-source network automation tool that has been developed to assist the "Network & Infra Security" team in their daily operational work. It validates whether newly proposed security policies already exist. Built entirely in‑house, the tool enhances operational efficiency, strengthens policy validation workflows, and contributes to maintaining a resilient organizational security posture. This project was developed under the supervision of Md. Imranul Islam (Lead Engineer) and Mohammad Zafar Ullah (Senior System Engineer). Their oversight ensured technical quality and alignment with organizational objectives.

